create a maven project 
mvn archetype:generate -DgroupId=com.mkyong.rest -DartifactId=resthelloworld -DarchetypeArtifactId=maven-archetype-webapp -DinteractiveMode=false

add eclipes capabality
mvn eclipse:eclipse -Dwtpversion=2.0

update pom.xml with the follwoing dependencies

<dependencies>
 
		<dependency>
			<groupId>com.sun.jersey</groupId>
			<artifactId>jersey-server</artifactId>
			<version>1.8</version>
		</dependency>
 
	</dependencies>



